{
  "page": "Manfryd Yew",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yew\" title=\"House Yew\"><img alt=\"House Yew.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/50px-House_Yew.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/75px-House_Yew.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/100px-House_Yew.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Manfryd Yew</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yew\" title=\"House Yew\"><img alt=\"House Yew.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/50px-House_Yew.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/75px-House_Yew.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d0/House_Yew.svg/100px-House_Yew.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Yew\" title=\"House Yew\">House Yew</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Manfryd Yew</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knight</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Yew\" title=\"House Yew\">House Yew</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfryd_Yew&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfryd_Yew&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Manfryd is part of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daven_Lannister\" title=\"Daven Lannister\">Daven Lannister</a>'s force at the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>. Manfryd and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raynard_Ruttiger\" title=\"Raynard Ruttiger\">Raynard Ruttiger</a> are given the command of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boom_(navigational_barrier)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Boom (navigational barrier)\">boom</a> across the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> that prevent any escape from the castle. They are also supplied with nets to fish from the river.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Despite their efforts, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a> manages to escape <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> by swimming downriver during a <a href=\"/index.php/Moon\" title=\"Moon\">moonless</a> night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manfryd_Yew&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Jaime V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"